      <p>OK, so I did a similar thing last week when I came home and found my husband sprawled out on the bedroom floor.  He was reaching for something under the bed but I had flashes in my brain that were much, much worse. There were actually tears when he stood up. Imaginations are tough little critters, aren&#39;t they?</p>
<p>Hope he heals quickly!</p>
<p>Now, am I the only one wondering what the home improvement store did when a customer gashed his thumb on a sharp piece of metal?</p>
    </div>

